                        <interp inst="t18491029-name-1096" type="given" value="MARY ELIZABETH"></interp>MARY ELIZABETH KNEBB</persName>
                  </hi>. I am single—I was present at Waterloo Church last Christmas day, and saw the prisoner married to Sarah Harriett Perkins.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was not aware what I was about at the time of my first marriage; I was intoxicated.</p>
